Acetylsalicylic acid is a very common cause of accidental poisoning in young children. It should be kept out of reach from young children, toddlers, and infants [FDA label].', '["B01AC06", "C07FX04", "C10BX04", "M01BA03", "N02BA71", "C10BX02", "B01AC56", "N02AJ07", "N02AJ02", "N02BA01", "C10BX05", "N02BA51", "A01AD05", "C10BX01", "C07FX03", "N02AJ18", "C10BX12", "C10BX08", "C10BX06", "C07FX02"]', '[]');
